Description: Provides tools for processing and analysing high-resolution archival tag datasets. Includes functionality for handling depth, temperature, 3-axis acceleration, 3-axis magnetometer, and 3-axis gyroscope data. Additional features for integrating and analysing video data from onboard cameras.
